{"about_the_game":"In Picterra you explore a colourful world full of interesting flora, fauna, and fungi to document with your camera and notebook.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Uncover what happened before</h2>You are dropped into an unknown world and asked by a mysterious force to restore its memories of what the world is like. By adding pictures to your scrapbook you return lost knowledge to your guide, which they use to give you various items that help you explore even further.<br>Discover the story of what happened to the people of this world by restoring balance to the old powers that protect it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make your notebook your own</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975750/extras/ProgressTracker-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter__1_.gif?t=1731315675\" /><br>Decorate pages with stickers, pictures and your own notes.<br>Keep track of your progress in photographing the world and name the creatures you've discovered.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become friends with cute creatures</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975750/extras/TreeRam-ezgif.com-speed__1_.gif?t=1731315675\" /><br>Learn how the creatures interact with each other and the world and use this knowledge to create picture opportunities and solve environmental puzzles.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731315675","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975750/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731315675","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975750/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731315675","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975750/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731315675","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_descrip